title: Dávid Kovács (footballer, born 1991)
text: Dávic Kovács (born 18 June 1991) is a <a href="Hungary">Hungarian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a> who plays for <a href="Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20I">OTP Bank Liga</a> club <a href="Budafoki%20MTE">Budafoki MTE</a>.
